io.libraft.agent
Interface CommandDeserializer

public interface CommandDeserializer

Implemented by a class that converts the binary representation of a Command into its corresponding Java object.

Implementations must be thread-safe. Ideally, calls to deserialize(java.io.InputStream) would not modify any internal state.

Method Detail

deserialize

Command deserialize(InputStream in)
                    throws IOException
Deserialize the binary representation of a Command from an InputStream into its corresponding Java object.

Implementations can assume that the complete binary representation of Command can be read from in without blocking.

Parameters:
in - InputStream from which to read the serialized Command
Returns:
a valid Command instance
Throws:
IOException - if there was an error reading from in or deserializing the binary stream into a Command instance
